-motivation","line":13,"column":0,"depth":2},"dream-game-elements--inspirations":{"type":"header","text":"Dream Game Elements / Inspirations","value":"dream-game-elements--inspirations","line":16,"column":0,"depth":2},"game-seedsideas":{"type":"header","text":"Game seeds/ideas","value":"game-seedsideas","line":28,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["bfbwiweiqyjetuxcxnztxqp","2fdt0zsteynlm6ax8wr7k3x","ky5tluzq147no964ecygqsa","5r68hrhtzgby2p3sdd7frq0","fgv47j66eib8kliuryycpne","tx8js1g1xi2urs8j8p3xm3v","d5gu2skes3tpz4vuidhqwaf","izlq0whl2ovb3b6bjz8zjwh"],"parent":"ckpt5dqzm4fv2ysnyyqi5q7","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"game-development\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#game-development\"></a>Game Development</h1>\n<h2 id=\"used-engines--tools\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#used-engines--tools\"></a>Used Engines &#x26; Tools</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/2fdt0zsteynlm6ax8wr7k3x\">DragonRuby</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"my-motivation\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#my-motivation\"></a>My Motivation</h2>\n<p></p><p></p><div class=\"portal-container\">\n<div class=\"portal-head\">\n<div class=\"portal-backlink\">\n<div class=\"portal-title\">From <span class=\"portal-text-title\">My Motivation</span></div>\n<a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/ky5tluzq147no964ecygqsa\" class=\"portal-arrow\">Go to text <span class=\"right-arrow\">→</span></a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"portal-parent-anchor\" class=\"portal-parent\" markdown=\"1\">\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-top\"></div>\n<div class=\"portal-parent-fader-bottom\"></div><p><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"block-anchor anchor-heading icon-link\" id=\"^main-line\" href=\"#^main-line\"></a>I like building things and I like people using things I made and enjoying using them. </p>\n</div></div><p></p><p></p>\n<h2 id=\"dream-game-elements--inspirations\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#dream-game-elements--inspirations\"></a>Dream Game Elements / Inspirations</h2>\n<p>Independent and not necessarily related or having to be used together</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\"Real\" Dynamic Time Travel mechanic - simulate the changes in the past and reconstruct the world (Steins;Gate)</li>\n<li>A hub where characters gather, a place/city/area they call home (DS9, Future Gadget Lab)</li>\n<li>Random bizarre craziness (Rick and Morty's dimensions)</li>\n<li>\"Floating\" islands on pillars (<strong>that</strong> project)</li>\n<li>Kirby RPG</li>\n<li>The extraordinary hidden in plain sight / parallel magic/fantasy society (Harry Potter and others)</li>\n<li>Intelligent agents, AI, especially symbolic AI</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"game-seedsideas\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#game-seedsideas\"></a>Game seeds/ideas</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/fgv47j66eib8kliuryycpne\">The \"perfect\" time travel game</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/bfbwiweiqyjetuxcxnztxqp\">Boss Design</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/2fdt0zsteynlm6ax8wr7k3x\">DragonRuby</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/d5gu2skes3tpz4vuidhqwaf\">Inbox</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/ky5tluzq147no964ecygqsa\">My Motivation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/5r68hrhtzgby2p3sdd7frq0\">Practicing an Art</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/izlq0whl2ovb3b6bjz8zjwh\">Resources</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/fgv47j66eib8kliuryycpne\">The \"perfect\" time travel game</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/digital-garden/notes/tx8js1g1xi2urs8j8p3xm3v\">Tips from an Producer</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/\">Home</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"w4mxpqpj9ftyo6pw17k3wj6","title":"Home","desc":"","updated":1655543408062,"created":1648806032875,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"not